Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE LANDING OF SOVEREIGN ROCK CASTLE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:01:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for you, King Romos.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:02:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This world summit\Nis a wonderful idea, Princess Leona.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,King Romos, he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a friend of Dai's now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,King Romos...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,King Romos! This! The Crown of Champions!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we make this into a weapon?!\NWe're making an Orichalcum sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That is already yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I oppose to remaking it\Ninto a weapon for world peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Bengana's ship is entering port!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a large ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Leona, I've come\Nanswering your summons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,King Bengana, we specifically\Nasked of you to be discreet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Using such a warship is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And what are those weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They're tanks, King Romos.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The pride of my country,\Nthe elite Tank Brigade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Akhim?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! The Bengana Tank Brigade takes pride\Nin being the world's strongest army!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.54,0:03:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all about weapons now. Swords\Nand magic are nothing against a cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This world summit is a war council on how\Nmy army will attack the Dark Army, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So where's it being held?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Please follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess not every king is very admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine,\NI know this is a bad time, but we...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry and go. Papunica still has me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it also has them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it! Let me rest a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! What do my eyes see,\Nbut Papunica Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're landing there,\NI'd have preferred a more impressive boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to look the part of a Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We decided to change our ways and\Ntry to be a real Hero's party, didn't we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Papunica's putting up a good fight with\Nthe Dark Army, so it should work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We can defeat the Dark Army\Nand become real heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If we stick with them and fight a bit,\Nwe should get some money and experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to Papunica!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No objection!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Landing... cancelled!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No objection!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How goes the Hero's Sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.92,0:05:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Same as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.67,0:05:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He tossed the Crown in the furnace\Nand is still staring at Dai's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already been half a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows what he's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.01,0:06:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Ron Berku...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Long ago, people and weapons were one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,People strove to match up\Nto powerful weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,People were strong,\Nand so weapons evolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.37,0:06:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now they're all worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You will show me the most powerful being\Npaired with the most powerful weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Jank, give me a hand.\NThis will be a big job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,At last!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's started!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron's started forging the sword\Nlike he's possessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help him,\Nso don't break his concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, this sword is a new life\Nbeing created specifically for Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So it won't be like forging\Nan ordinary weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That's why he was studying\Nthe hands that would wield it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They say a true weapon\Nchooses its wielder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Dad. You've got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need you to tell me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Meruru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I see it! I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A giant shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A terrifying... A terrifying power!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.62,0:07:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, Papunica will fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,King Bengana, as we've said,\Nwe must gather the world's forces as one
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to defeat the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we've all gathered here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And my army will lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying to relax and leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,King Bengana,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ringaia was a powerful country\Ncalled the "Fortress Kingdom,"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,yet we fell before the Dragon Legion\Nof the Dark Army in one week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Their power can only be understood\Nby those who fought them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies,\Nbut your country still exists
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,only because the enemy has not yet\Nbrought in their full force.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You insult me, General Bowson!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you not know the power of my army,\Nthe world's greatest army?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is going nowhere. Even after\Nwe finally managed to hold this summit...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Observe!\NThat cutting-edge, top-class warship!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That unstoppable Tank Brigade!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what forces\Nthe Dark Army may have, they can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:10:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!\NI don't know, but I do know this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Papunica is finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That face! Sovereign Rock Castle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So Hyunckel's hypothesis was right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sovereign Rock Castle itself\Nis a walking fortress! A giant Overfiend!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That said...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't believe how big it is!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A giant! A giant is attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! How did something that big\Nget so close without you noticing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there was a thick mist\Nover the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A mist?! Did you say a mist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Bengana's ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as Hadorra suspected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The world leaders\Nare gathered here in Papunica.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic ants who defy King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll smoke them out and crush them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:23.57,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}BEHOMA{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NHEALING-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:28.58,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}TOMAKUGUTSOSHO{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What a creature!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable!\NIt's beyond human comprehension!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be here to wipe us all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They knew about this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Akhim! Take command of the Tank Brigade!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Show them the true power\Nof the Bengana Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! As you command!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so reckless, King Bengana!\NIt destroyed a warship with one attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My tanks! My tanks won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll blow that lump of rock to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not just a giant made of rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Sovereign Rock Castle!\NThe main fortress of the Dark Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.81,0:12:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,To face it head-on\Nwill only mean pointless death!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,His Majesty has ordered me\Nto display Bengana Army's true power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Win or lose, we must show our courage\Nto lead the rest of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He seemed unpleasant at first,\Nbut he has his own loyalties.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sense a warrior in him.\NI can't let him die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.19,0:12:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:13:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait! It's finally complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That's my Vortex Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The life of legendary weapons,\Nthe Magic Jewel was undamaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.44,0:13:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So I rebuilt it using Papunican metals!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.61,0:13:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I call it Vortex Axe Returns Mark II!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! This'll give me\Nthe strength of a hundred!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.49,0:13:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the strength of a thousand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you!\NI'll join you in a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good. I can't use\Na crystal ball like Grandmother can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That was enough.\NAll we needed was a glimpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Something big is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to Papunica!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.77,0:13:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten?!\NThis sword is being made for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's being given life for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a normal weapon! It has a soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A sword with a soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When it answers your soul\Nand accepts you as its wielder,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.80,0:14:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,it will unleash\Nthe world's greatest power!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you must\Nbear witness to its birth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll come back for it.\NCan't you make it in the meantime?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A blade requires\Nthe voice of its wielder's soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Without that voice, this will become\Njust another weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron Berku is pouring his life into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It must take godly strength beyond our\Nunderstanding to create this sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He's using a material like Orichalcum.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a normal forging.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But at this rate, Papunica...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Dai, you stay here\Nand complete your sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, we'll hold off the Dark Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to work together\Nto defeat an enemy of that size!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you have to stay here, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They're trying to kill\Nall the world leaders at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We need your Hero's Sword now\Nmore than ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.33,0:15:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you think we can't even\Nbuy you some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.29,0:15:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,After all we've been through,\Nyou can't possibly think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.13,0:15:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the deal!\NLeave things to us for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue firing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Weigh anchor and keep firing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was pretty cool what I said back there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't back down now having said all that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I really might get killed this time\Nfighting something that big.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.03,0:16:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's freaking out, Miss Maam.\NAre you sure about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:17:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp can seem unreliable at first,\Nbut he always overcomes pain and fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how he's always been.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! No point in chickening out!\NTake the bull by the horns!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's all go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, try to be useful to Ron Berku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.69,0:17:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! And you better not\Nget in everybody's way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Show 'em what you're made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Rura!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Stein...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp's gone away again, hasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:18:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've never seen Popp\Nwith such a serious look in his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone and grown up all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.65,0:18:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,As a kid he used to always be\Nsuch a wimp and a quitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When he left home,\Nwe were angry at Master Aban, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We should thank him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,for making our boy into a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,See that?! See that?!\NThe force of the invincible Bengana Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We can win this, my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:18:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess, where's the giant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:18:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The bay! How did you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Meruru showed us! So we hurried back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Dai?! I thought he was with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.67,0:19:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's making the world's strongest sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be ready soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.59,0:19:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So we came back first\Nto try to hold them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget your "world's strongest sword!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'd need that?! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My Bengana Tank Brigade\Nwill soon blow that giant to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's not working.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you see it's breaking apart,\Ndropping pieces of rock everywhere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.12,0:19:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But in that smoke,\Nits energy hasn't waned at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Cease fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be nothing left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Abandon ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A castle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.69,0:20:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You fools.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You've revealed it by yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sovereign Rock Castle's true form.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Princess of Papunica, Leona...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and other world leaders.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I serve the great Dark King Ban.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am Shadow Legion Commander Mystban.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.85,0:21:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadow Legion Commander Mystban...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So it really was him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I bring you an order.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.94,0:21:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he going to threaten us,\Nsaying come out or die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.19,0:21:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are all worthless.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.91,0:21:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You are vermin to Dark King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender will not be allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.38,0:21:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Begone from this world,\Nalong with this entire country!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you face the devil\NWith logic on your side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:07.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatoe akuma ni seiron kazashite\Nmukatte mitemo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may just be a rationalization{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:11.35,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sore wa akumade seitouka\Nsashite chigai wa naikamo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now, even now I waver{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:15.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima mo ima mo yureteiru kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far will we go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:19.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wa dokomade yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard a voice like an angel's whisper{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:22.78,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tenshi no sasayaki nimo nita\Nkoe ga kikoeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it was an imposter's illusion\NIt still rang in my ears{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:26.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hatamata petenshi no mayakashi\Nhitokiwa mimi ni hibiiteita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exposed to love and sorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:30.41,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni hiai ni sarasare nagara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the path strewn with pride{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:34.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hokori mamire michi no tochu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fleeting moments of cowardice{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:38.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kiete wa ukabu touhikou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The SOS I held back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:42.54,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nomikonda SOS{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I clenched my trembling fist{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:48.13,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}furueru te wo nigirishimeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That single little promise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:53.72,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatta hitotsu no chiisana yakusoku ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those trivial little memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:57.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}honno sasaina omoidetachi ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:22:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're still in my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:22:59.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}itsumade tattemo kono mune wo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As embers that keep me burning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:03.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kogashi tsuzukeru tomoshibi ni naru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A single transparent beam of light{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:08.49,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitosuji no toumei na hikari ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lights the way before me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:11.66,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}me no mae wo terashite yuku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is little that I can do{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:16.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku ni dekiru koto wa ikutsu mo naisa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just keep on to the future\NI managed to grasp through my faith{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:22.54,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shinjinuita saki ni te ni shita mirai wo\Nsusunde yuke{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Shadow Legion appears\Nwith Sovereign Rock Castle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As Dai waits for his sword to finish,\NPopp and the others fight without him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the enemy's forces are endless.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.65,0:23:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mystban himself appears\Nand attacks using his Dark Aura.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.19,0:23:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The next showdown begins in Papunica.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.91,0:23:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.16,0:23:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Master of Darkness Against His Pupil"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.12,0:23:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.12,0:24:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,
